Properties":{"id":"20240924142108-9qysm3u","updated":"20240924142307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以止损要是硬指标，那也是亏损 10% 以内要考虑的了，拖久了亏损幅度大了，就没啥用了；"}]},{"ID":"20240924142321-bncvu92","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924142321-bncvu92","updated":"20240924143115"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果买的宽基指数基金，比如沪深300，中证A50，中证100，中证A500这些，买到指数基金的底部区域，可以不用止损，只要慢慢的加仓摊薄成本就好了；这个需要做好仓位控制和对大趋势的判断，买到任何产品的高点都是很难办的；"}]},{"ID":"20240924141031-yefwb0o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240924141031-yefwb0o","updated":"20240924141144"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亏损后的回本所需涨幅计算公式：1 ÷ ( 1 - 亏损比例 ) - 1 = 回本需要涨"}]},{"ID":"20240924140706-hsg55u2","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[2,2],"Properties":{"colgroup":"|width: 97px;","id":"20240924140706-hsg55u2","updated":"20240924141511"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亏损比例"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"回本需要涨"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10%"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11%"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20%"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"25%"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"30%"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlign":2,"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"42.86%"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","TableCellAlig